      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it was first manufactured. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no imperfections, scratches, or chips of any kind. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather and materials showing zero signs of wear and still retaining that new-car scent. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained to the highest possible standards. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly collector-grade example that is indistinguishable from new.",
