    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition and represents the pinnacle of its class. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep shine and absolutely no scratches, dings, or chips. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with leather upholstery that looks and smells brand new and every electronic feature functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound, offering a smooth, powerful ride with a complete service history and no pending maintenance needs. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for a showroom-quality vehicle.",
