    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion for weekend trips and daily commutes alike! It's in really solid shape and has been well-maintained over the years. You\u2019ll love how smoothly it handles the road. It\u2019s ready for its next adventure\u2014could that be with you? Come take it for a spin!",
