      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0-liter naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery up to an 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox, the drivetrain is complemented by a factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal lateral dynamics. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the high-strung valvetrain remains robust. The chassis retains its composure via Electronic Damper Control (EDC), while the carbon fiber roof panel lowers the center of gravity for improved turn-in response. This is a driver-focused example with a clean subframe and consistent compression across all cylinders.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
