      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents an exceptional opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-documented driver. The exterior finish remains vibrant, showing only the lightest signs of road use, while the body panels are straight and free of significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the upholstery is free of tears, the dashboard is crack-free, and every electronic component\u2014from the climate control to the infotainment system\u2014operates as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises, benefiting from a strict adherence to its factory maintenance schedule. Recently fitted with a fresh set of tires and having passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection, this car is ready for the open road. It offers the perfect blend of pride of ownership and everyday functionality.",
      "price": 34800.0,
